<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer to See What Could Be</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Jul 04, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
God of Love,
</p>

 <p>
When I see a stranger, <br></br>
do you see a beloved child?
</p>

 <p>
When I see an enemy, <br></br>
do you see a friend?
</p>

 <p>
May I see what is, <br></br>
and not what I fear might be.
</p>

 <p>
Even more, <br></br>
may I see what could be, <br></br>
if I were to give even a fraction <br></br>
of the grace that I have received.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


